articles.title: US House votes to censure Rashida Tlaib over Israel-Hamas war comments - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: House votes 234-188 to reprimand Tlaib, the only Palestinian American in Congress, who said she would not be silenced.
articles.content:
The United States House of Representatives has voted to censure Rashida Tlaib, the only Palestinian American in Congress, over her comments on the Israel-Hamas war.
